    "description": "In this game you will have the experience of returning to the happiness and sweetness of your childhood, you will calmly go through all kinds of danger and nothing bad will happen to you, just trust that you are capable of achieving it.<br>When you reach a score of 50,000, a good message awaits you!!!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the gameplay:</h2>• This is an arcade-style casual game;<br><br>• The player has his score increased over time;<br>• To keep the score increasing, the player needs to dodge a rain of bombs that fall non-stop and collect bonus lives that drop every 15 seconds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182710/extras/7d9cfb0507d6b59b4040f77d45e5be9f.poster.avif?t=1767728752\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182710/extras/7d9cfb0507d6b59b4040f77d45e5be9f.webm?t=1767728752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182710/extras/7d9cfb0507d6b59b4040f77d45e5be9f.mp4?t=1767728752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2>• Bonuses to increase speed and lives that help the game's performance;<br><br>• Score multiplier bonus up to 10 times over time during a match;<br>• Increased amount and speed of bombs that fall over time, making the game more challenging during a match;<br>• Relaxing soundtrack and pleasant sound effects;<br>• Various visual effects and changes in brightness according to 4 (four) phases of the day: morning, noon, afternoon and night, for visual satisfaction and game contemplation;<br>• A book with ancient wisdom in the pause menu, translated into three languages ​​(Portuguese (Brazil), Spanish and English);<br>• 443 Toy-based Skins, with 22 skins unlocked with the maximum score obtained in matches;<br>• The game saves your overall record and keeps the maximum score achieved.",
